    <div class=3D"vs-question__blurb">
     =20

      <p class=3D"lead"><span class=3D"highlight">What=E2=80=99s better</sp=
an>, a native app or a web app for design work? It=E2=80=99s 2024, so we sa=
y why choose? Don=E2=80=99t restrict yourself with a design tool that=E2=80=
=99s limited to only web tech. With Sketch, you get the best of both worlds=
.</p>

<h4 id=3D"truly-native">Truly native</h4>
<p>Our native app for designers offers great features that web-based electr=
on apps, like Figma, simply can=E2=80=99t. That means super-fast performanc=
e on Apple silicon, native font rendering and P3 color profiles.</p>

<h4 id=3D"with-the-power-of-the-browser">With the power of the browser</h4>
<p>Share your designs with our powerful web app. Invite collaborators to yo=
ur documents, then give and get feedback in any browser, on any operating s=
ystem.</p>

<p>Developers, project managers and other team members get the tools they n=
eed. A focussed environment for every stakeholder means Sketch is easier to=
 learn and easier to use, with less distractions. Keep your workflow simple=
.</p>

